{
  "stem": "18061.4",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] But it came over there, there was everything, even with Jewish people, were such kind that the German knew everything what's going on.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We have between our Jewish people also, betrayers.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Informers, right.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, we didn't know it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But they were.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "After that, we, we know it is.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And when the Germans find out there was supposed to be an escape from some people, [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] they tried to get some people off it.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] And when another escape, from three people, also one of them from our group escaped with them-- [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] and what had happened after 10, 12 days, he came back to the camp.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "For what I don't know.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "When I spoke to him, he said, he came back to show the road how to escape from Treblinka, and to get in-- into Warsaw and other places.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And came back, yes.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Through the gate.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They didn't had an accurate list of people.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because, let's say, from the barrack when they went to work, 400 people.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "At least 25, 30 got shot.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So the exact list, the exact name they didn't had.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "His name was Rosenthal.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "His first name was Lebo.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That's what he said.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I wouldn't say.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Maybe came back to, to take money.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But he was in touch with the-- with the commandant.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And he was having a meeting with the commandant all night in the barrack.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And he told the commandant how to escape through barbed wires.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The Jewish, Galewski.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] A day after he got from Galewski, and he got from kapo [?",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Rakoski ?] a lot on money.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he escaped again.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
